    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《隐域突击》</strong> 抛弃了“所见即所得”的传统射击逻辑，引入了前所未有的“<strong>动态视野博弈</strong>”。战场中心初始是一片虚无，你掌握独特的“双弹药系统”，用显形子弹揭露地图，用致命火力终结敌人。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【核心玩法】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不是一款无脑冲锋的游戏，你的弹匣里装填着两种截然不同的弹药：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👁️ <strong>显形子弹 ：</strong>命中隐匿区域后，通过声纳脉冲技术短暂地“显示”命中范围内的地形及掩体。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥 <strong>伤害子弹 ：</strong>常规弹药，用于消灭敌人。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你必须时刻做出生死决策：是消耗显形子弹获取地图信息？还是凭借对地图的<strong>记忆</strong>盲射压制？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1053880/extras/8cfb223d0ad1e5cc5214d3c36cd3575a.poster.avif?t=1768011983\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1053880/extras/8cfb223d0ad1e5cc5214d3c36cd3575a.webm?t=1768011983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1053880/extras/8cfb223d0ad1e5cc5214d3c36cd3575a.mp4?t=1768011983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【游戏特色】</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🕵️ 独创“隐域”机制</strong>：打破传统射击游戏的视野依赖。玩家需要空间记忆力来“脑补”战场全貌。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🎮 UE5 极致画质</strong>：得益于虚幻引擎5的 <strong>Lumen</strong> 全局光照与 <strong>Nanite</strong> 虚拟几何体技术，从隐形状态到显形状态的无缝切换。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🤝 5v5 深度战术协作</strong>：单打独斗在这里行不通。小队需要精细分工：谁负责“开灯”侦查？谁负责火力覆盖？谁负责侧翼包抄？沟通与配合是胜利的唯一钥匙。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>⚡ 动态交互道具</strong>：战局胶着？去寻找散落在地图角落的交互道具吧！获取它们将赋予你特殊的战术优势——从提升移动速度、增加显形范围，到短时间的隐身，显示全地图轮廓等。合理争夺这些道具，往往能瞬间扭转战局。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1053880/extras/095454e769a1729d988d92f164e2fca1.poster.avif?t=1768011983\" aria-label=\"场景道具\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1053880/extras/095454e769a1729d988d92f164e2fca1.webm?t=1768011983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1053880/extras/095454e769a1729d988d92f164e2fca1.mp4?t=1768011983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【自定义地图】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不满足于官方战场？<strong>提供基于 UE5 的地图编辑器</strong>，游戏支持加载编辑器导出的地图数据。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏗️<strong> 自由搭建：</strong> 利用游戏中的资产，亲手搭建你的战术竞技场。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📏 <strong>定义规则：</strong> 你可以自定义哪些区域是永久隐形，哪些是可见。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌐 <strong>社区共享：</strong> 将你的杰作上传至创意工坊。</p></li></ul>",
